value.0: A worker at the Eddington estate.

A rather haughty and competent mage, Lady Eddington is curt with the common folk but keen to take on prospective students and foster arcane talent within any she can.

She seems more concerned and troubled since she returned from Greengarden.
Set into a copper band is a single green eye, constantly scanning the area and blinking now and then.  When the eye spots something, a faint tingle can be felt in the ring finger.

The Order Silver Dragon Knights are an elite force of warriors that serve the Crown, often acting directly on the orders of the Lord Commander or Regent. They are law keepers and defenders of the innocent, always serving the ideals of the Triad and Bahamut above all else.

The Silver Dragons serve and protect the people, acting as the first line of defense against would-be villains and criminals.

The Mages are a small but well-trained unit within the Kingdom of Kohlingen. The symbol of Mystra emblazoned on their cloaks, they work diligently as a branch of the Silver Dragons, under the command of the Magister.
This is a settlement guard insignia for the guard templates.

The Rangers are a specialized branch of the Silver Dragons whom boast great skill in archery, tracking, and scouting. With the potential threats lurking in the wilderness surrounding the kingdom, they play a vital role in keeping the people safe.
